&lt;li&gt;Data Rate: 1Mbps to 150Mbps down and up&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Realtek RTl8192cu Chipset&lt;/li&gt;
&lt;li&gt;Dimensions: 19 x 14.3 x 6.2mm&lt;/li&gt;
